{"tid":1900150,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[行動post 推上熱門] 星期六 831 半周年網上集會 一齊支持被捕手足","createTime":"2020-02-27T05:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T11:19:41.000Z","uid":42194,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"8b14facc0cee76679b117f31dac8eacc9fb7f06d","tid":1900150,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JfJGtrr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJfJGtrr.jpg&h=82839790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「疫症當前 警暴蔓延」831半周年網上集會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n形式暫改 初心不變<br />\n2.29 網上集會 直播要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n日期：2月29日<br />\n時間：7pm-9pm<br />\n直播媒體：<br />\n民間集會團隊FACEBOOK<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCATeam%2F&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=8e81197e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/</a><br />\n民間集會團隊YouTube<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IbQYg5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IbQYg5&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=1153901a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IbQYg5</a><br />\n<br />\n星期六係2月29日<br />\n係咩意義？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">係8.31 半週年呀！</span><br />\n除左去太子站悼念外，仲可以做D 咩？<br />\n就係參與網上集會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次集會特別邀請左響8.31嘅被捕手足<br />\n同黃色音樂人去表演，成日支持黃色經濟圈，我地係時候都多D 支持黃色音樂圈啦<br />\n<br />\n大家唔係唔支持呀？<br />\n8.31襲擊被捕手足包括：<br />\n中大女生吳傲雪<br />\n教大學生會會長梁耀霆<br />\n<br />\n音樂圈手足包括：<br />\n莊正<br />\nTommy阮民安<br />\nCasey何君俊<br />\n「尖沙咀肥媽」李嘉晉<br />\n<br />\n警暴受害手足：<br />\n教育實驗學社成員黃子悅<br />\n及多區親證警暴嘅區議員等<br />\n<br />\n希望大家星期六晚<br />\n一齊重燃抗爭嘅熱心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"8df4c1abc934bb9a0b145688952fd6e74715bb69","tid":1900150,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:11:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n星期六晚見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ecae3a54d26248842354070dbea03487d1ffca","tid":1900150,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:11:45.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n星期六晚見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f446725a5cc50a5276e3fc44fe9fc8d25e96d08","tid":1900150,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:12:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81ccec7b3b3aba381ca26957a8dca7fed3209681","tid":1900150,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:13:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n星期六晚見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb290888c6bafda918a8c7e19d83d0ad6807c96","tid":1900150,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:19:29.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n星期六晚見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2382cac09b3c0e364cda87e6ad1b10ff3779900e","tid":1900150,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:21:04.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n星期六晚見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fb3b857a3fa27d8696ffff092d2e96d2a4b2a5","tid":190